            <lg xml:id="TK1106">
<l>uṟutō ṟuyirtaḷirppat tīṇṭalāṟ pētaik </l>
<l>kamiḻti ṉiyaṉṟaṉa tōḷ</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The shoulders of this fair one are made of ambrosia, for they revive me with pleasure every time I embrace them.</l>
